[ Upstream commit d1bc560e9a9c78d0b2314692847fc8661e0aeb99 ]

Add nested locking with I_MUTEX_XATTR subclass to avoid lockdep warning
while handling xattr inode on file open syscall at ext4_xattr_inode_iget.

